{"tid":1586413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【警渣想移民？我需要笑嗎？】","createTime":"2019-09-22T02:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:26:11.000Z","uid":276437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9ce56eba6c145a18d93e5ae8d9e0f6471254de","tid":1586413,"uid":276437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"【警渣想移民？我需要笑嗎？】<br />\n<br />\n太遲㗎嘞，想有一條生路，轉做污點證人啦。<br />\n<br />\n【針對警渣的白宮聯署 x 3】<br />\n<br />\n請美國國會禁止香港警察移民或入境美國<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=0779864a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署請求美國拯救香港巿民，作人道救援<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=82e730c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a><br />\n<br />\n全面制裁香港警渣<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-police&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=f55bb56d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police</a><br />\n<br />\n簽＞查電郵＞確認簽署＞搵十個人簽<br />\n<br />\n來源：新唐人電台<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/09/17/a102666475.html/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F09%2F17%2Fa102666475.html%2Famp&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=e81b9fbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/09/17/a102666475.html/amp</a>"},{"pid":"e61044da961a2449237e09959f34a90286340546","tid":1586413,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8c7c77a328b06d2444df67e4433f44370390e6","tid":1586413,"uid":276437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUFF8S4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUFF8S4.jpg&h=311320a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a08bf6f61c540002be2147f88fa27d70b3b2c09","tid":1586413,"uid":276437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"【向聯合國人權理事會呈請投訴香港警察】<br />\n<br />\n不知道大家有沒有留意連登，有一個「港女A」不停在連登吶喊尋人，求各位警暴受害者可以提供詳細資料，以佐證她提交到聯合國人權理事會的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n「港女A」是我從前任教中學時的舊生，依然常聯絡、深得我心、我十分信任也關係親厚的舊生。她身材太嬌小、做不到衝衝子；但人小志氣大，她一直在想自己可以怎樣貢獻自己的力量呢？於是就做了這一件事。<br />\n<br />\n香港警暴已經不是一小撮受害人的事，而是整個香港都會受害、有普通香港市民也吃過苦頭的問題了。就算街坊未呼吸過催淚氣體，也有被黨鐵／警察無理封路而影響吧？<br />\n<br />\n現在「港女A」的呈請已到最後階段，她需要各位香港人以聯署人身份參與、支持這份送到聯合國人權理事會的呈請。<br />\n<br />\n如有問題，歡迎PM。我會把你的PM傳遞給「港女A」。留言裡有「港女A」一直以來的連登post link。最後，多謝「港女A」和她的拍檔V，辛苦了。謝謝你們！<br />\n<br />\n老實講，威力大過白宮聯署的，大家幫幫手！！！懇請各位聯署、廣傳。多謝各位。聯署呈請的link如下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdLootBz6B7Jp291b_zekxwXtV8ESGE3bvQgf3N35K7PSeJmQ/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2JbdtfqiXOaxT9uVqeUpEgDok9VZcnB-y0ygofPa5DkOs_IxqXnluzlGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdLootBz6B7Jp291b_zekxwXtV8ESGE3bvQgf3N35K7PSeJmQ%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2JbdtfqiXOaxT9uVqeUpEgDok9VZcnB-y0ygofPa5DkOs_IxqXnluzlGk&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=52b3d22f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdLootBz6B7Jp291b_zekxwXtV8ESGE3bvQgf3N35K7PSeJmQ/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2JbdtfqiXOaxT9uVqeUpEgDok9VZcnB-y0ygofPa5DkOs_IxqXnluzlGk</a>"}]}